{
  "texts": [
    "Such valuable information is encoded within the rubrics.",
    "However, prompt-specific models fail to account for these attributes.",
    "GPT for holistic score: Several studies investigated the use of large language model for AES (Mizumoto and Eguchi 2023; Yancey et al. 2023; Mizumoto and Eguchi 2023, 2023) conducted a study exploring the application of GPT-3 for AES on the TOEFL11 dataset (see Sect. 6.4).",
    "The authors examined the GPT model's ability to score essays by inputting the prompt, rubric and essay.",
    "The model then predicts a score category of Low, Medium, or High."
  ]
}